description:
I'm a young at heart woman....I can be serious...I can be fun....hoping some enchanted evening to meet the right stranger, and there will be that spark...
I'm a Fashion design. I think everyone has a unique and awesome story to tell...every life is full of so much adventure.... the dragons we faced, the good, bad and, ugly times we had to deal with...and God was there for us in it all...
I like to keep life simple..
